body_html:
Thanks @drpngx. The previous Jenkins error was caused by //tensorflow/tools/api/tests:api_compatibility_test. This is expected as we switch tf.unique from Unique to UniqueV2.

I have run API golden and updated the PR:

bazel-bin/tensorflow/tools/api/tests/api_compatibility_test
           --update_goldens True

I think the Jenkins should pass now.

body:
Thanks @drpngx. The previous Jenkins error was caused by `//tensorflow/tools/api/tests:api_compatibility_test`. This is expected as we switch `tf.unique` from Unique to UniqueV2.

I have run API golden and updated the PR:
```
bazel-bin/tensorflow/tools/api/tests/api_compatibility_test
           --update_goldens True
```

I think the Jenkins should pass now.
